you know, you did, I think,

08:21.794 --> 08:23.060
when you were little.

08:24.130 --> 08:25.662
I was going through a hard time.

08:25.698 --> 08:29.066
You were this little five
year old guy playing piano,

08:29.102 --> 08:32.369
trying to help his
hysterical mother calm down.

08:32.404 --> 08:34.037
I don't remember you being hysterical.

08:34.072 --> 08:38.475
